OL,7,FFour former police officers are under
OL,8,Finvestigation for gross misconduct
OL,9,Fcharges in the case of a man wrongly
OL,10,Fjailed for rape, the police watchdog
OL,11,Fhas revealed.
OL,13,FOne is also under criminal
OL,14,Finvestigation for potential misconduct
OL,15,Fin public office and perverting the
OL,16,Fcourse of justice.
