OL,3,CPolice officers under gross misconduct
OL,4,Cinvestigation in wrongful conviction
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FHe consistently maintained he did not
OL,8,Fcommit the assault, and twice applied
OL,9,Fto the Criminal Cases Review Committee
OL,10,Fbefore new evidence proved his
OL,11,Finnocence, and he was finally
OL,12,Facquitted in 2023.
OL,14,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC) has taken up complaints
OL,16,Fthat Mr Malkinson made and has
OL,17,Fconfirmed four retired officers at
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police may face
OL,19,Fgross misconduct charges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
