OL,4,Cinvestigation in wrongful conviction
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FIOPC Regional Director Catherine Bates
OL,8,Fsaid: "Mr Malkinson is a victim of one
OL,9,Fof the worst miscarriages of justice
OL,10,Fin British history.
OL,12,F"We continue to work hard to ensure
OL,13,Fhis complaints are thoroughly and
OL,14,Findependently investigated.
OL,16,F"Following a detailed review of
OL,17,Fevidence spanning a period of more
OL,18,Fthan 20 years, we have now informed
OL,19,Ffour retired GMP officers that they
OL,20,Fare under investigation for potential
OL,21,Fgross misconduct.
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
