OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,F"We will continue to keep Mr Malkinson
OL,8,Fand GMP updated on our progress."
OL,10,FToby Wilton, of Hickman & Rose, who is
OL,11,Frepresenting Mr Malkinson in relation
OL,12,Fto his police complaint, said: "Twenty
OL,13,Fyears on from Mr Malkinson's wrongful
OL,14,Fconviction no police officers have yet
OL,15,Ffaced any sanction for their role in
OL,16,Fthe miscarriage of justice that he
OL,17,Fsuffered, Greater Manchester Police
OL,18,Fare yet to admit their responsibility
OL,19,Ffor what happened, and he is yet to
OL,20,Freceive any compensation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@aO]tD@`OU
