OL,7,F"This announcement that four officers
OL,8,Finvolved will now face a misconduct
OL,9,Finvestigation, and one will now face
OL,10,Fcriminal investigation, is an
OL,11,Fimportant first step ` but it is vital
OL,12,Fthat all those responsible at Greater
OL,13,FManchester Police, as well as the
OL,14,Fwider force, are held to account."
OL,16,FThe IOPC says that some of the areas
OL,17,Fthey are focusing on are:
