OL,7,FThe IOPC also added serving an officer
OL,8,Fwith notice they are under
OL,9,Finvestigation does not necessarily
OL,10,Fmean that disciplinary proceedings or
OL,11,Fcriminal charges will follow.
OL,13,FIt said at the end of the
OL,14,Finvestigation, it will determine
OL,15,Fwhether there is an indication that
OL,16,Fanyone serving with the police may
OL,17,Fhave breached the standards of
OL,18,Fprofessional behaviour or if the case
OL,19,Fshould be referred to the Crown
OL,20,FProsecution Service.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
