OL,4,Cinvestigation in wrongful conviction
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FMr Malkinson, from Grimsby, had his
OL,8,Fconviction quashed by the Court of
OL,9,FAppeal in July 2023.
OL,11,FHe twice applied for his case to be
OL,12,Freferred for appeal by the Criminal
OL,13,FCases Review Commission (CCRC), but
OL,14,Fwas turned down.
OL,16,FMr Malkinson was eventually released
OL,17,Ffrom prison in December 2020.
OL,19,FThousands of convictions are now being
OL,20,Freviewed in the wake of his case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
